Policy-Hi Repository License Summary

This repository combines artifacts under multiple licenses:

1. Code under `scripts/eval/`:
   MIT License (see below).

2. Structured benchmark data under `data/policies.json`, `data/regions.json`,
   and `paper/data/personas.json`, `paper/data/ground_truth.json`,
   `paper/data/deployment_stats.json`, `paper/data/judge_accuracy.json`,
   `paper/data/results/`:
   Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0).
   The policy *contents* are derived from publicly published Korean government
   welfare-policy descriptions (복지로 / 정부24 / 지자체); the 15-tag structured
   annotations, region normalization, and persona/ground-truth files are the
   contribution of the authors and released under CC BY 4.0 with the same
   attribution requirement.

3. Paper LaTeX sources under `paper/tex/` and `paper/refs.bib`:
   (c) the authors. Reuse with attribution; redistribution of compiled PDFs
   subject to the workshop venue's policies at camera-ready.

